 there are three important materials that a link or chain can be made out of,
 and the corresponding crystals are called:
 
\emph on
muon-fluoride chain crystals
\emph default
,
 
\emph on
muon-nitrite chain crystals
\emph default
,
 and 
\emph on
nilmuonic chain crystals
\emph default
.
